#datos originales
data <- read_csv("../data/resultados/dataset_2013a2020.csv", 
    locale = locale(encoding = "ISO-8859-1")) %>%
  filter(anio %in% c(2016:2019)) %>%                     # filtro aos para mayor velocidad
  mutate(fecha =  yearmonth(paste(anio, mes, sep="/")) ,
         n_dias = days_in_month(fecha),
         prod_pet = prod_pet/n_dias,
         prod_gas = prod_gas/n_dias,
         prod_agua = prod_agua/n_dias) %>%           # CONVERSION A UNIDADES DIARIAS
  select(-n_dias)

Default

  model(stl = STL(prod_pet)) %>% 
  components()

dcmp_crudo %>%
  as_tsibble() %>%
  autoplot(prod_pet, colour="gray") +
  geom_line(aes(y=trend), colour = "#D55E00") +
  geom_line(aes(y=season_adjust), colour = "#0072B2") +
  labs(
    y = "m3/da",
    title = "Produccin de crudo"
  )


dcmp_crudo %>% autoplot()


dcmp_gas = prod_tot %>% 
  model(stl = STL(prod_gas)) %>% 
  components()

dcmp_gas %>%
  as_tsibble() %>%
  autoplot(prod_gas, colour="gray") +
